00:00:13.321 --> 00:00:18.902
Hi! Namaste! Welcome to your favorite show, Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:30.141 --> 00:00:34.983
What are you cooking for us today?
Green Gram &amp; Vermicelli Dessert (Payasam)

00:00:43.031 --> 00:00:45.592
Ingredients required to make Green gram &amp; Vermicelli Dessert

00:00:45.699 --> 00:00:49.627
Green Gram, Vermicelli, Sago, Jaggery, Milk

00:00:50.162 --> 00:00:53.067
Cashews, Almonds, Dates &amp; Ghee

00:00:54.753 --> 00:00:57.942
Let's learn how to make the green gram &amp; vermicelli dessert

00:01:07.373 --> 00:01:10.621
Take a cooking pan and pour some water and let it come to boil

00:01:20.262 --> 00:01:24.893
Soak the green gram and the sago in water for about 2 hours

00:01:34.321 --> 00:01:41.162
First, add half a cup of soaked green gram and cook for 10 minutes

00:02:05.573 --> 00:02:09.296
Now, add half a cup of the soaked sago into the pan

00:02:23.343 --> 00:02:26.335
Close the lid

00:02:31.366 --> 00:02:41.727
Once boiled, remove the lid and pour some milk and wait 5 minutes

00:02:51.433 --> 00:02:58.000
Now, add a cup of ghee toasted vermicelli and cook for 5 minutes

00:03:54.617 --> 00:03:58.983
Add 250 gms of jaggery syrup

00:04:18.868 --> 00:04:20.353
Add some cardamom powder for flavor

00:04:36.834 --> 00:04:42.006
Once done, garnish with the almonds, dates and the ghee toasted cashews

00:04:44.894 --> 00:04:46.414
And it's ready to serve

